sql:
SELECT name
FROM instruments
ORDER BY name ASC;

external_knowledge:
- Top financial instruments refer to those with the highest total volume traded; 
- Last month is defined as the time period between the current date and one month prior to the current date.
- The ranking system assigns the highest rank (1) to the instrument with the highest total volume, the second-highest rank (2) to the instrument with the second-highest total volume, and so on.
